                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17540530-6-defend96 t17540530-6-deflabel23"></join> on the first of this month, and on Thursday the 16th she made her elopement: I missed the sheet on the 13th, the gown on the Wednesday following, and the shirt she took from me the day she went away. She confessed where she had pawned them, and we have them all now.</p>
